modName: CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible
summary:
another skin texture for CBBE & CHSBHC,and vanilla body or other body using vanilla UV map
femfeet compatible
descriptionHtml:
MOST RECENT UPDATE:

NOTE for people who seek permission to use my texture:
I give permission, just credit me as usual, no need to directly contact me as I might not be around.

NOTE for people who seek help with my texture installation:
- if you want older files, they are in old file download.
- larger face texture also there, just browse through it, use common sense, I would not be here often to reply individual problem anymore. 

May 15, 2012
-Basvanbeu muscletexture changer lite pack with my skinset, choose inside the pack which body mesh you use CBBE  or UNP/vanilla, then install inside data folder, and activate esp.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/MSDUX.jpg[/IMG]
it gives variation to the female npc and player character based on their bodyweight, this light version only has 4 entries activated in the esp, however I packed 11 different combinations that can be activated if desired but there would be some performance impact on memory usage 

Hair mods I use:
Tera Hair Pack, Apachii Sky Hair (available at nexus), Lovely Hairstyles(available at nexus), KKK Hair (available at nexus), Ren Hair.

I use this ENB setting:
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1752

===================================================================================
>This is a skin texture mod for: 
-Caliente\'s CBBE v2 & v3 female body
-Vanilla body (or other body who use vanilla UVmap) like: Thepal & Dimon UNP female body
-Vanilla body for 4uDIK RB female body
-Face texture for female character
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Lu8n8.jpg[/IMG]

===================================================================================
>CBBE skin installation guide:
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Nw3pl.jpg[/IMG]
-instal Caliente CBBE v3 mesh first:  http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666
-instal my mod inspect the folder structure, open \"CBBEuser\" folder install the content into \"Data\" folder

===================================================================================
>Vanilla skin installation guide:
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/z1xeI.jpg[/IMG]
-instal Thepal\'s Nude female mesh first: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=70
-instal FemFeet v3: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3666
-instal my mod inspect the folder structure, open \"UNP or Vanilla users\" folder copy the content into \"Data\" folder
or
-instal Prometheus Better Female Natural Body mesh first: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7198
-instal FemFeet v3: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3666
-instal my mod inspect the folder structure, open \"UNP or Vanilla users\" folder copy the content into \"Data\" folder
or
-instal Dimon99\'s Dimonized UNP first: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709
-instal my mod inspect the folder structure, open \"UNP or Vanilla users\" folder copy the content into \"Data\" folder
or
-instal 4uDIKs Real Body first: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6667
-instal FemFeet v3: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3666
-instal my skin mod (Vanilla skin 4uDIKs RB compatible) 
==================================================================================
>People who has problem with custom texture not showing after installing hires pack that came with ck, please read Caliente\'s instruction about it
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666 


==================================================================================
>Version history:
v1
initial version 

v1.1
fixed hip seams, fit CBBE v2 slim and normal

v1.2 hairy
hairy pubic and pits, fixed breast side to fold more naturally and smoother. 

v1.3 all in one pack
comes with hand texture, femfeet texture, hairy or non hairy option.

v1.3 all in one pack for V3 with changed hip
comes with hand texture, femfeet texture, hairy or non hairy option.

v1.4 all in one pack
universal skin that support CBBE v2 and v3 available in hairy and shaved

v1.4 vanilla conversion all in one pack
vanilla UVmap with vanilla and femfeet support, currently will fit with: Vanilla mesh (will have vanilla undies covering the naughty parts), Thepal\'s Nude Females, and Dimon99\'s UNP body.

patches for v1.4
-muscular normal map for CBBE skin texture v1.42 blended with vanilla male muscle
-more seamless hand texture for Vanilla and CBBE skin texture v1.4

v1.5 vanilla conversion all in one pack
vanilla UVmap with vanilla and femfeet support, currently will fit with: Vanilla mesh (will have vanilla undies covering the naughty parts), Thepal\'s Nude Females, and Dimon99\'s UNP body.
muscle patch and fixed hand texture included

v1.6 CBBE and Vanilla skin
both dealing with seams on hip, ankle an wrist
-vanilla breast normal map follows UNP pattern on the center and a mix between my own and UNP for the outer side, to make it more natural when worn by UNP 

optional patch for CBBE skin v1.6 for muscular normal map with less visible veins

v1.7 vanilla skin
-more seamless
-fixed textures positioning (belly button, crotch, nipple, ankle)
-upgraded femfeet texture from v2.2 to v3, the same version packed with UNP body 
-no longer available in non femfeet/ standard feet
-head texture v1.7 would be its ideal pair with seamless neck http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5106
-very old female edited to look less wrinkly and with femfeet normal map 
-less veins for optional muscle body normal map patch

patches for v1.7
-v1.71 add femalebody_sk.dds for people who didn\'t have it from another previous nude mods
-v1.72 due to demand, I make compatibility for Bella\'s Better Female face mod, as universal patch for CBBE and vanilla skin, I also include my own facial texture map that match the new skin lightness. 
-v1.73 hairy & dirty body patch for both CBBE & vanilla/UNP  

Reupload revision:
v1.7 rev1 (both CBBE & vanilla)
-fixing ankle seams
-femalebody_sk.dds is now included

v1.72 rev1 Bella\'s face compatibility patch (both CBBE & vanilla)
-fixing chest texture.

v1.8
for Vanilla and CBBE body, in separate packs for people who instal it with auto installation, and also face texture in one place, to limit confusion. 
- remake for the hair, I made it longer and curlier somewhat, I will upload the hair resource later,
or you can make that with size 1 brush and then set the brush to fade in 40pixels then either using pen tool or free hand with mouse or stylus draw each hair.
- changing specular map for the face
- add some dirt level to the skin more in the un-shaved version, and cleaner for the strip and shaved version
- I make the pectoral area paler, and add subtle veins on the breast, however the strip and shaved version is less pale since they bare their chest more under the sun obviously. 
- new specular for hands, reduce the hand seams. 

v1.8 rev
-revised the face make the cheek area lighter.
-released fuller lips face texture as separate version.

v1.8
- 4uDIKs Real Body compatible Vanilla skin texture, added to main file

v1.8 face with makeup patch added
CBBE and Vanilla/ UNP:
v1.8 lite version body and face
v1.8 muscle patch v2 with more abs 
v1.8 smooth arm and toned abs normal map patch for Vanilla/UNP & CBBE added

using Phnx method:
http://tesadventures.com/forum/index.php?topic=4082.0
I saved my girls face into face preset, replacing 3rd face on the list, as people PM me requesting how to make some of my girls face, I guess this would be much simpler answer:
-choose the third face and you get my chars\' faces
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/CMKNM.jpg[/IMG]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/A2qSJ.jpg[/IMG]

v1.9 integration with Basvanbeu Muscle Texture Changer lite version based on the old version used with permission.
Basvanbeu has a new system that will have more skin variation based on race with the new mod, the new mod still being completed, and I supply my skin for it as well so this will work as a lite teaser of Basvanbeu mod, and also major simplifying the installation process of my skin mod.
a link to Basvanbeu new mod would be revealed after Basvanbeu is ready with the newest version.  
==================================================================================
>My  credit list:
- Caliente for CBBE body mesh, and for the skin I partially use around the hip seams
- Dimon 99 for UNP body mesh, part of nipple texture in UNP compatible vanilla skin, and for using vanilla UVmap.
- Thepal for Nude Females body, that is still the most compatible body for most armors.
- YoZj/4uDIK for the awesome seamless texture I used as my template to work on.   
- Basvanbeu for Muscle Texture Changer system

==================================================================================
>Please help me with screencaps
I play with small screen resolution because my monitor is old, so feel free to post your screencaps.
showing the good or the bad, but please inform me then in the image title what skin version you use there.


thank you
